00:08:04.090 --> 00:08:07.210
And this is documented it
was such a major development

00:08:07.210 --> 00:08:10.700
in the world economy that it's not
just something to be documented

00:08:10.700 --> 00:08:13.550
in narrow Russian sources.

00:08:13.550 --> 00:08:16.830
