00:24:57.350 --> 00:25:01.610
It was also equal to 100
poods of Siberian coal.

00:25:01.610 --> 00:25:05.740
And there was coal in the
[inaudible] as I mentioned.

00:25:05.740 --> 00:25:10.470
[Inaudible] coal was less
rich as an energy source

00:25:10.470 --> 00:25:12.490
