00:25:12.490 --> 00:25:17.270
So one cubic sazhen it took
150 poods of [inaudible] coal

00:25:17.270 --> 00:25:20.780
to equal one cubic sazhen of wood.

00:25:20.780 --> 00:25:25.070
There was some very
low-grade coal near Moscow.

00:25:25.070 --> 00:25:28.070
That was the only coal that
the regime had access to.

00:25:28.070 --> 00:25:32.820 position:56%
And so coal from Moscow, it took 250
poods of coal from the Moscow basin

00:25:32.820 --> 00:25:34.980
to equal one cubic sazhen of wood.

00:25:34.980 --> 00:25:38.690 position:56%
And then what is very, very
interesting is it took only 70 poods

00:25:38.690 --> 00:25:43.130
of oil to be the equivalent
of cubic sazhen of wood.

00:25:43.130 --> 00:25:48.770
So I'm also going to mention just
