00:30:18.960 --> 00:30:24.800
by really late 1919, the Civil
War in effect is over militarily,

00:30:24.800 --> 00:30:31.250
there's a war separately
between Soviet Russia and Poland.

00:30:31.250 --> 00:30:33.590
But in terms of the white armies

00:30:33.590 --> 00:30:36.430
that whether they had
democratic roots

00:30:36.430 --> 00:30:40.180
